  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An Endless runner with a twist! Play as a dog named PRIN-C1 who can walk, trot and run but cannot stop. </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Go Slow. Go Fast. Speed is your choice</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/1074962c8faa7efb8b43ea625bd79c2d.poster.avif?t=1773571083\" width=660 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/1074962c8faa7efb8b43ea625bd79c2d.webm?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/1074962c8faa7efb8b43ea625bd79c2d.mp4?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Switch views seamlessly</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/7f3f98fa227bef8a770eddeff2f5b785.poster.avif?t=1773571083\" width=660 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/7f3f98fa227bef8a770eddeff2f5b785.webm?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/7f3f98fa227bef8a770eddeff2f5b785.mp4?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect treats. If not.. steal them</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/172800aa0014e868d484e95fc6d97815.poster.avif?t=1773571083\" width=660 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/172800aa0014e868d484e95fc6d97815.webm?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/172800aa0014e868d484e95fc6d97815.mp4?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Smash them or get punched</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/ec0e225b1ecbf8a7de83ac41771a4d7b.poster.avif?t=1773571083\" width=660 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/ec0e225b1ecbf8a7de83ac41771a4d7b.webm?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/ec0e225b1ecbf8a7de83ac41771a4d7b.mp4?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock fun costumes by completing score challenges</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/b61d1e23238d294116604e41e819bb63.poster.avif?t=1773571083\" width=660 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/b61d1e23238d294116604e41e819bb63.webm?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610970/extras/b61d1e23238d294116604e41e819bb63.mp4?t=1773571083\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
